text: Gymnacranthera canarica is a species of plant in the family Myristicaceae. It is native to Karnataka and Kerala in India. ==References== * World Conservation Monitoring Centre 1998. Gymnacranthera canarica. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 21 August 2007.
